the Commission stated that they impaired its ability to evaluate the applicant's qualifications under the public
interest standard, and that conclusion was compelled by the cumulative impact of each uncompleted section. In 
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=28 g=1 f=3 -->
